ns and merger and restructuring advice to management teams and boards of directors which is based on our view and knowledge of both the public and private real estate capital markets kimberlite works with owners who have real estate operating capabilities within traditionally defined industry segments and emerging segments such as medical  medical office self storage and student housing and who have a track record of performance which allows for qualification as an institutional fiduciary how to reach us contact us  park avenue th floor new york ny   send us a message expertise  kimberlite expertise kimberlite provides senior level advisory and institutional capital raising services to global asset managers institutional investors financial sponsors and family offices kimberlite places the needs of its clients first in a culture that values integrity professionalism and excellence with a focus on the highest ethical standards in creating longterm value for clients focused boutique investment bank your trusted advisor – continued dislocation turmoil and strategy shifts amongst traditional investment banks have left numerous management teams and boards without a “trusted advisor” at a time when such counsel is in high demand kimberlite represents a team of experienced professionals devoted to the needs of underserved areas of the market lines of service kimberlite provides independent conflict free advisory services to key relationships across the globe in the following areas capital structure review and advisory strategic alternatives assessment and implementation advisory to management teams and boards of directors regarding acquisitions sales mergers corporate restructurings and initial public offerings capital raising for growth or restructuring opportunities between bestinclass operators and global institutional investors loan restructuring negotiations learn more about real estate how to reach us contact us  park avenue th floor new york ny   send us a message c